<ion-header [translucent]="true">
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>
      Tab 2
    </ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content [fullscreen]="true">
  <ion-header collapse="condense">
    <ion-toolbar>
      <ion-title size="large">Tab 2</ion-title>
    </ion-toolbar>
  </ion-header>

  <ng-container *ngFor="let item of links">
    <ion-list>
      <ion-item-sliding>
        <ion-item>
          <ion-label>Category:{{item.category}}, blacklistFlag:{{item.blacklistFlag}}, type:{{item.type}}</ion-label>
        </ion-item>

      </ion-item-sliding>
    </ion-list>
  </ng-container>
</ion-content>
import { Component } from '@angular/core';
import {StorageService} from "../services/storage/storage.service";
import {Link, LinkService} from "../services/link/link.service";
import {Observable, of} from "rxjs";



@Component({
  selector: 'app-tab2',
  templateUrl: 'tab2.page.html',
  styleUrls: ['tab2.page.scss']
})
export class Tab2Page {

  links: Link[] = [];

  constructor(
    private linkService: LinkService

  ) {
    this.linkService.links$.subscribe(links => {
      this.links = links;
    })
  }

  /*private initLinks() {
    this.linkService.links$.subscribe(links => {
      this.listData$ = [];
      links.forEach(link => {
        this.listData$.push(of(link));
      });
    });
  }*/


}
